            <div class="ind-detail-hero-sub">Financial services businesses in the UAE \u2014 including banks, exchange houses, investment managers, insurance companies, and DIFC/ADGM-licensed entities \u2014 operate under some of the most demanding compliance frameworks in the world. AML obligations, DFSA or FSRA licensing requirements, ESR for financial services Relevant Activities, and UAE Corporate Tax rules for financial institutions all interact in ways that require specialist expertise.</div>
