            <div class="ind-pain-card"><h5>DFIC/ADGM accounting \u2013 different from UAE mainland</h5><p>DFSA and ADGM regimes require IFRS based financial reporting and specific prudential disclosures that differ from some mainland practices, and firms that do not align their accounting can struggle at regulatory reviews.</p></div>
